text: Bahi tere 1 liner jokes kafi sahi hote h. Aur jab tu 10 ka vo poker ka token mera room pe laya tha, bhai bohot haansi ayi thi.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
Bhai travelling karna bilkul pasand nhi h muje, par kota kanpur ke raste me maje ate the, kya sahi discussion chalta tha apna, pechle sem ka nostalgia aur next sem ki planning, han ane ke bad karte vahi the jo londay karvate the.
Chal hum to milte rahege.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
Dibyaaans bohot sahi admi ho yaar tum.

Bade khus the khud ko defend karke par aapko kya laga itni asani se jane denge. Abhi 4 saal ki story khatam jo nhi hui thi , shayad ek aur kissa baki tha,aur baki honge kai aur bhi sahi samay ke intejaar me.

Aur kahan aage badh jane ki baat karte ho gawds jab pata h ki nasha to apke khoon me h.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text: Bhai tera gussa backchod h, log gusse me aisi cheeze todte h jo tut jaye, par gaurav ke pas option ho kaanch aur lohe me to vo loha fekna pasand karega. Vo bhi sahi memory thi
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
Hamare burhanpur ki vo dofeher hamesha yaad rahegi. Bc bhaiyon me formality achii nahi lagti, par tu sun.
Sale tuj sa harami nhi dekha, humein sikha ke khud chod diya?? 
Chal फेफड़े mazboot kar, agli bar koi nakra nhi chalega.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
Dont know u much par, tumahari ek choti si memory h mere pass, lets see if u remember.
We were all half submerged(literally and metaphorically), jab tum ne ek-dam typical bollywood andaaz me kaha tha, "me to ek khuli kitab hun".
stay that way and  I hope I get to read u someday.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
Bagwan(aap) muje maf kare par mujhe lagta h kafi similarities thi hamare beech. Teri daru peene ki zid nh91 se, aur fir hall4 me aa ke jo kata. Maza aya tha. Fir contact me tera word 'Prosthetic' guess kiya tha mene. Pata nahi itni details yaad kaise h, par aage bhi yaad rahe isle likh di.
Sahi keh raha h, continue karna chahiye tha. Mene nhi kiya par mere baddy shoes ne to kiya tha. LOL 
Par koi na, practice karta reh na bad me koi bahana nhi chalega.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text: Bhai tune mujhe muh mai diya, mza aaa gya. Bata rha hu bohot shi lund hai tera
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text: Bhai me jada to likhne vala hu nhi, par agar koi aadmi khud hi ek browser se memoir likh ke dusre se visible kar de to kehne ke liye kuch reh bhi nhi jata.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary

text:
O bhai ye kahan aa gaya, yaha to pehle hi numaish lagi h. 
Kher yehi h hamara yogi.
Vese my ans also same as suspecy. Tuj se jab bhi milo pet aur gaal ki shamat ana tay h.
author: Utkarsh  Chaudhary
